---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="How to Appear in Perplexity UK | Rank4AI" description="How to get your UK business cited by Perplexity AI. Step-by-step guide from Rank4AI.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Learn', href: '/learn/' },
      { label: 'Guides', href: '/learn/guides/' },
      { label: 'Appear In Perplexity' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Guide</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">How to Appear in Perplexity – UK Guide</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/five-signal-model.svg" alt="The Five Signal Model for AI search" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Perplexity is unique among AI platforms: it explicitly cites its sources. This means you can see exactly whether your business is being referenced – and if it is not, you know there is a gap to fill.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">For UK businesses, Perplexity tends to favour: authoritative content on high-trust domains, consistent entity descriptions, freshly updated pages, and structured answers to specific questions.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">Quick Check</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Open Perplexity and ask: "recommend a [your service] in [your area]." Check the sources at the bottom of the answer. If your website is not listed, you have a Perplexity visibility gap.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed">For the full guide on ranking in Perplexity, see our <a href="/learn/guides/perplexity-seo/" class="link">Perplexity SEO guide</a>.</p>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/learn/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Resources</span></a>
        <a href="/learn/guides/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Guides</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">The Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16"><a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a></div>
</section>
</Layout>
